OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 16 Jun to Thu 25 JunFA
OL,6,Fchangeable period is likely through
OL,7,Fthe middle of next week with outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain focused across the north and
OL,9,Fnorthwest, some of which could spread
OL,10,Fto parts of the south and southeast at
OL,11,Ftimes. Some strong winds could
OL,12,Faccompany this, although with
OL,13,Ftemperatures generally above normal.
OL,14,FInto the following weekend, high
OL,15,Fpressure will probably become more
OL,16,Fdominant with conditions turning more
OL,17,Fwidely dry and settled, and probably
OL,18,Fvery warm for many, especially in the
OL,19,Fsouth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
